Then, how do you know about it?

00:18:04.018 --> 00:18:07.755 position:24% line:83% align:start
Because I, myself,
am a previous Red Star holder.

00:18:08.823 --> 00:18:12.426 position:7% line:83% align:start
So what you're saying is I have
to become a fake Seven Star?

00:18:12.560 --> 00:18:13.995 position:35% line:83% align:start
[ICHINOSE]
Yes. We'll sell it like,

00:18:14.127 --> 00:18:16.296 position:19% line:83% align:start
"Transfer student gets
record-breaking test scores,

00:18:16.430 --> 00:18:17.999 position:10% line:89% align:start
surpassing even the Empress."

00:18:18.131 --> 00:18:19.968 position:35% line:83% align:start
Or perhaps
"A new genius appears,

00:18:20.100 --> 00:18:23.270 position:19% line:83% align:start
making it to Seven Star
on his very first day!"

00:18:24.839 --> 00:18:26.608 position:35% line:83% align:start
Of course,
you don't have to do this.

00:18:26.741 --> 00:18:30.444 position:27% line:83% align:start
You can decline.
The choice is entirely yours.

00:18:30.578 --> 00:18:31.879 position:10% line:89% align:start
If red's just not your color,

00:18:32.013 --> 00:18:34.414 position:16% line:83% align:start
then pack up your things
and leave the island.

00:18:34.549 --> 00:18:37.150 position:19% line:83% align:start
We'll say you leveraged
an illegal ability

00:18:37.284 --> 00:18:39.453 position:21% line:83% align:start
against the Empress,
nullifying the match.

00:18:39.587 --> 00:18:42.222 position:16% line:83% align:start
But do you really want it
to end like that?

00:18:42.356 --> 00:18:44.191 position:16% line:83% align:start
Didn't you have a reason
for coming here?

00:18:44.324 --> 00:18:47.160 position:38% line:83% align:start
-A goal?
-[HIROTO] Yes.

00:18:47.294 --> 00:18:48.563 position:27% line:89% align:start
I do have a goal.

00:18:49.429 --> 00:18:51.365 position:5% line:89% align:start
There's someone I have to find.

00:18:52.232 --> 00:18:54.334 position:10% line:89% align:start
I can't accept a bad ending.

00:18:54.468 --> 00:18:55.903 position:7% line:89% align:start
If you give up now, it's over.

00:18:56.037 --> 00:18:58.573 position:16% line:83% align:start
In fact, you'll probably
never see her again.

00:18:58.706 --> 00:19:00.374 position:16% line:83% align:start
Sounds like you've really
thought this all through.

00:19:00.508 --> 00:19:01.876 position:35% line:83% align:start
[ICHINOSE]
No.

00:19:02.010 --> 00:19:04.646 position:13% line:83% align:start
This is as much a surprise
to me as to anyone else.

00:19:04.779 --> 00:19:07.515 position:27% line:83% align:start
But I'm quite the
ambitious woman at my core.

00:19:07.649 --> 00:19:09.416 position:19% line:83% align:start
If an opportunity falls
into my lap,

00:19:09.550 --> 00:19:11.753 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'm hardly going to pass it up.

00:19:12.419 --> 00:19:14.287 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
Play the part, huh?

00:19:16.189 --> 00:19:18.726 position:16% line:83% align:start
If that's what it takes.
I'll do it.

00:19:20.193 --> 00:19:22.096 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:19:22.964 --> 00:19:25.833 position:10% line:83% align:start
[laugh] That was incredible!
The sheer audacity!

00:19:25.967 --> 00:19:27.835 position:35% line:83% align:start
I don't see
what's so funny about it.

00:19:27.969 --> 00:19:30.104 position:10% line:83% align:start
"As long you don't mind being
absolutely crushed

00:19:30.237 --> 00:19:32.740 position:19% line:83% align:start
and humiliated in front
of the entire student body."

00:19:32.874 --> 00:19:35.109 position:16% line:83% align:start
-You're making fun of me.
-No, not at all!

00:19:35.242 --> 00:19:37.344 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'm cheering for you. [laughs]

00:19:37.477 --> 00:19:39.881 position:19% line:83% align:start
But in all seriousness,
that was a master-class

00:19:40.014 --> 00:19:41.348 position:10% line:89% align:start
in psychological subversion.

00:19:41.481 --> 00:19:42.684 position:27% line:89% align:start
You're a natural

00:19:42.817 --> 00:19:44.152 position:27% line:83% align:start
at disconnecting
your inner feelings

00:19:44.284 --> 00:19:45.920 position:19% line:89% align:start
and outward appearance.

00:19:46.054 --> 00:19:49.023 position:10% line:83% align:start
Scouting you for this academy
was clearly a stroke of genius.

00:19:49.157 --> 00:19:50.190 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:19:50.323 --> 00:19:51.592 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
So, um, question.

00:19:51.726 --> 00:19:53.260 position:13% line:83% align:start
Where am I supposed to live
from now on?

00:19:53.393 --> 00:19:54.629 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ICHINOSE] Oh,
I've arranged a dorm for you.

00:19:54.762 --> 00:19:56.396 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'll send the coordinates
to your Device.

00:19:56.531 --> 00:19:57.397 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
Appreciate it.

00:19:57.532 --> 00:19:58.900 position:33% line:89% align:start
See you soon.

00:19:59.033 --> 00:20:00.668 position:10% line:83% align:start
Looking forward to your next
great performance!

00:20:00.802 --> 00:20:02.670 position:24% line:83% align:start
"If you don't mind
being absolutely crushed

00:20:02.804 --> 00:20:03.705 position:27% line:89% align:start
and humiliated."

00:20:07.942 --> 00:20:10.210 position:24% line:89% align:start
A red lie. [sighs]

00:20:12.613 --> 00:20:15.583 position:30% line:83% align:start
Hey. You know,
that was a wonderful speech

00:20:15.717 --> 00:20:17.217 position:5% line:89% align:start
you gave at the ceremony today.

00:20:17.350 --> 00:20:18.586 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
How did you?

00:20:18.720 --> 00:20:20.621 position:41% line:83% align:start
[SARSA]
It's plastered all over Stoc.

00:20:20.755 --> 00:20:23.256 position:5% line:89% align:start
So, what is it you want exactly?

00:20:23.390 --> 00:20:24.659 position:21% line:89% align:start
You found my weakness

00:20:24.792 --> 00:20:26.326 position:24% line:83% align:start
and thrust yourself
into the spotlight.

00:20:26.460 --> 00:20:28.261 position:16% line:83% align:start
And yet you still haven't
exposed my secret?

00:20:28.395 --> 00:20:29.864 position:24% line:89% align:start
What're you doing?

00:20:29.997 --> 00:20:32.533 position:16% line:83% align:start
Gathering more attention
before you absolutely crush me?

00:20:32.667 --> 00:20:36.637 position:41% line:83% align:start
Please.
I'm begging you. Don't.

00:20:37.337 --> 00:20:40.875 position:7% line:83% align:start
I know I have no right to ask.
I know I'm being selfish,

00:20:41.008 --> 00:20:43.410 position:21% line:83% align:start
but I have my reasons
for doing this.

00:20:43.544 --> 00:20:47.014 position:5% line:83% align:start
Reasons for keeping up this lie.
Whatever the cost.

00:20:47.148 --> 00:20:49.684 position:13% line:89% align:start
So I'm begging you. Please.

00:20:49.817 --> 00:20:53.087 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'll do anything you ask,
just don't tell anyone, okay?

00:20:53.221 --> 00:20:54.555 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
Look, I'm sorry.

00:20:54.689 --> 00:20:56.991 position:24% line:83% align:start
But I have no idea
what you're talking about.

00:20:57.125 --> 00:20:58.391 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SARASA]
Quit playing dumb!

00:20:58.526 --> 00:21:01.095 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm not messing around here,
this is serious!

00:21:01.229 --> 00:21:02.262 position:27% line:89% align:start
I know you know.

00:21:02.864 --> 00:21:05.133 position:16% line:83% align:start
You wanna make me say it?
Fine.

00:21:05.265 --> 00:21:07.101 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'm not Sarasa Saionji!

00:21:07.235 --> 00:21:08.803 position:38% line:89% align:start
Say what?

00:21:11.239 --> 00:21:12.507 position:24% line:89% align:start
Are you satisfied?

00:21:12.640 --> 00:21:16.511 position:27% line:83% align:start
There. I said it.
I'm not Sarasa.

00:21:16.644 --> 00:21:18.646 position:19% line:83% align:start
I've been acting as her
double here for the past year,

00:21:18.780 --> 00:21:21.215 position:27% line:83% align:start
but my real name
is Rina Akabane.

00:21:21.348 --> 00:21:22.650 position:7% line:89% align:start
A whole year of winning games,

00:21:22.784 --> 00:21:25.186 position:19% line:83% align:start
knowing that if I lost,
my secret was out.

00:21:25.318 --> 00:21:27.420 position:16% line:89% align:start
And today, I lost to you.

00:21:28.222 --> 00:21:30.958 position:10% line:83% align:start
You took the Red Star from me
when you won the game.

00:21:31.092 --> 00:21:33.694 position:7% line:83% align:start
Which means you know the truth
that I was hiding.

00:21:33.828 --> 00:21:36.564 position:13% line:83% align:start
Are you saying the Red Star
comes with some kind of penalty?

00:21:36.697 --> 00:21:38.933 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SARASA]
Are you still playing dumb?

00:21:39.066 --> 00:21:41.536 position:24% line:83% align:start
The Red Star holder
gets to tell a lie, right?

00:21:41.669 --> 00:21:43.070 position:5% line:89% align:start
But if they lose it to someone,

00:21:43.204 --> 00:21:45.106 position:10% line:83% align:start
that person gets to find out
what lie they told!

00:21:45.239 --> 00:21:46.439 position:24% line:89% align:start
You must know that!

00:21:47.241 --> 00:21:50.044 position:10% line:83% align:start
After all, you're the holder
of the Red Star now.

00:21:51.212 --> 00:21:53.815 position:27% line:83% align:start
Listen, Akabane--
I mean, Saionji.

00:21:53.948 --> 00:21:56.617 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm afraid you've got
this whole thing wrong.

00:21:57.417 --> 00:21:58.719 position:13% line:89% align:start
Until you told me just now,

00:21:58.853 --> 00:22:00.688 position:19% line:83% align:start
I honestly had no idea
about your lie.

00:22:00.822 --> 00:22:02.723 position:5% line:89% align:start
I really did get here yesterday,

00:22:02.857 --> 00:22:05.726 position:5% line:83% align:start
and I really am still that inept
at using my Device.

00:22:05.860 --> 00:22:08.196 position:10% line:83% align:start
Also, this is the first time
I'm hearing of the Red Star

00:22:08.328 --> 00:22:09.764 position:19% line:89% align:start
having a disadvantage.

00:22:09.897 --> 00:22:12.567 position:13% line:83% align:start
No way! That can't be true!
You beat me so easily,

00:22:12.700 --> 00:22:14.702 position:19% line:83% align:start
and became a Seven Star
on your very first day!

00:22:14.836 --> 00:22:17.437 position:7% line:83% align:start
I guess it does look like that
on the surface, huh?

00:22:17.572 --> 00:22:20.107 position:27% line:83% align:start
But the truth is
I'm not a Seven Star at all.

00:22:21.441 --> 00:22:23.811 position:19% line:83% align:start
That's actually the lie
I'm telling.

00:22:23.945 --> 00:22:26.446 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm using the Red Star's effect
to boost my status.

00:22:26.581 --> 00:22:29.750 position:24% line:83% align:start
My legitimate rank
is only One-lousy-Star.

00:22:29.884 --> 00:22:32.253 position:13% line:83% align:start
All I've got is the red one
I took from you.

00:22:32.385 --> 00:22:33.821 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm as low rank as they come.

00:22:33.955 --> 00:22:35.723 position:27% line:83% align:start
I have my reasons
the same as you,

00:22:35.857 --> 00:22:38.092 position:21% line:83% align:start
so I'm having to lie
about my ranking.

00:22:40.528 --> 00:22:41.963 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SARASA]
Stop. Hang on.

00:22:42.096 --> 00:22:43.664 position:27% line:89% align:start
Hold up a second.

00:22:44.632 --> 00:22:46.067 position:16% line:89% align:start
Lemme get this straight.

00:22:46.200 --> 00:22:48.269 position:7% line:83% align:start
You're not the strongest person
on Academy Island,

00:22:48.401 --> 00:22:49.971 position:10% line:89% align:start
you won our game by accident,

00:22:50.104 --> 00:22:52.405 position:27% line:83% align:start
and you seriously
didn't know my secret?

00:22:52.540 --> 00:22:54.775 position:16% line:83% align:start
Yeah, that's more or less
the gist of it.

00:22:54.909 --> 00:22:57.745 position:13% line:89% align:start
But, then that would mean,

00:22:57.879 --> 00:22:59.981 position:10% line:89% align:start
I did all of this to myself?

00:23:00.514 --> 00:23:02.049 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
Woah, wait a minute.

00:23:02.183 --> 00:23:05.385 position:30% line:83% align:start
She's a double,
ergo she's not the real Empress.

00:23:05.519 --> 00:23:07.521 position:30% line:83% align:start
So, it follows
that she's not a daughter

00:23:07.655 --> 00:23:08.856 position:19% line:89% align:start
of the Saionji family.

00:23:08.990 --> 00:23:10.390 position:33% line:83% align:start
Which means,
even though I beat her,

00:23:10.524 --> 00:23:11.525 position:33% line:83% align:start
the director
would have no reason

00:23:11.659 --> 00:23:13.261 position:13% line:89% align:start
to be angry with me, right?

00:23:13.393 --> 00:23:14.695 position:5% line:89% align:start
So, why the heck did I even need

00:23:14.829 --> 00:23:17.131 position:19% line:83% align:start
to become a Seven Star
in the first place?

00:23:21.535 --> 00:23:25.072 position:13% line:89% align:start
/Eh. That's a dorm? Really?

00:23:25.472 --> 00:23:27.074 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's one thing after another.

00:23:27.375 --> 00:23:29.010 position:27% line:89% align:start
I mean, come on!

00:23:32.079 --> 00:23:33.848 position:35% line:89% align:start
'Scuse me.

00:23:34.749 --> 00:23:37.652 position:13% line:89% align:start
I welcome you home, Master.

00:23:40.154 --> 00:23:41.722 position:44% line:89% align:start
Woah.

00:23:42.823 --> 00:23:44.859 position:38% line:83% align:start
/[HIROTO]
Major cutie.

